subSubSection.paragraph:
Etymology .—The new species is named after the collector of the holotype specimen, Philippe Bacchet, a marine naturalist and photographer, co-author of the well-known “Guide des poissons de Tahiti et ses îles ” (
Bacchet et al . 2007
).
